# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string appears on the homepage of the Sim4Life.lite
# platform, highlighting its educational benefits and free access for
# students.
# website, providing an overview of the platform's purpose and availability
# for students.
# CTX-VERSION: cb62e56 2026-07-08T12:14:52Z
#: services/static-webserver/client/source/class/osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/S4LLiteSpecs.js:28
msgid ""
"        Sim4Life.lite is a powerful web-based simulation platform that "
"allows you to model and analyze real-world phenomena and to         design "
"complex technical devices in a validated environment. Sim4Life.lite has been"
" created specifically for students to         facilitate their understanding"
" of computational modeling and simulations for various topics, ranging from "
"wireless communication         to medical applications. The access to "
"Sim4Life.lite is available free of charge to students enrolled at registered"
" universities.      "
msgstr ""
"Sim4Life.lite es una potente plataforma de simulación basada en la web que "
"te permite modelar y analizar fenómenos del mundo real y diseñar "
"dispositivos técnicos complejos en un entorno validado. Sim4Life.lite ha "
"sido creado específicamente para estudiantes para facilitar su comprensión "
"del modelado computacional y las simulaciones para varios temas, que van "
"desde la comunicación inalámbrica hasta aplicaciones médicas. El acceso a "
"Sim4Life.lite está disponible de forma gratuita para estudiantes "
"matriculados en universidades registradas.      "

# CTX-INTERPRETATION: This string is a product description for Sim4Life.lite,
# highlighting its features and capabilities in scientific simulation.
# of a scientific simulation software's website, highlighting the features and
# capabilities of the Sim4Life.lite version.
# CTX-VERSION: cb62e56 2026-07-08T12:14:57Z
#: services/static-webserver/client/source/class/osparc/product/quickStart/s4llite/S4LLiteSpecs.js:37
msgid ""
"        <b>Sim4Life.lite offers</b><br>        - Framework (GUI, Modeling, "
"Postprocessing)<br>        - 3D modeling environment (based on the ACIS "
"toolkit) and CAD translators<br>        - Postprocessing and visualization "
"of the simulation results (2D and 3D viewers, 2D planar slice, volume "
"rendering, streamlines, surface fields on arbitrary 3D structures, radiation"
" and far-field data)<br>        - No restrictions on number of modeling "
"objects<br>        - Solvers & Tissue Models:<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-FDTD: "
"Electromagnetics Full-Wave Solver<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-QS: Quasi-Static "
"Electromagnetics Solver<br>        &emsp;- P-Thermal: Thermodynamic "
"Solver<br>        &emsp;- P-Acoustics: Acoustics Solver<br>        &emsp;- "
"T-Neuro: Neuronal Tissue Models<br>        - Computational anatomical model "
"Yoon-sun, the first Korean model of the IT’IS Virtual Population<br>        "
"- Material database<br>        - Python and Jupyter Notebook scripting      "
msgstr ""
"        <b>Sim4Life.lite ofrece</b><br>        - Marco de trabajo (GUI, "
"Modelado, Postprocesamiento)<br>        - Entorno de modelado 3D (basado en "
"el kit de herramientas ACIS) y traductores CAD<br>        - "
"Postprocesamiento y visualización de los resultados de la simulación "
"(visores 2D y 3D, corte plano 2D, renderizado de volumen, líneas de "
"corriente, campos superficiales en estructuras 3D arbitrarias, datos de "
"radiación y campo lejano)<br>        - Sin restricciones en el número de "
"objetos de modelado<br>        - Simuladores y Modelos de Tejido:<br>"
"        &emsp;- P-EM-FDTD: Simulador de Ondas Completas "
"Electromagnéticas<br>        &emsp;- P-EM-QS: Simulador Electromagnético "
"Cuasi-Estático<br>        &emsp;- P-Thermal: Simulador Termodinámico<br>"
"        &emsp;- P-Acoustics: Simulador Acústico<br>        &emsp;- T-Neuro: "
"Modelos de Tejido Neuronal<br>        - Modelo anatómico computacional Yoon-"
"sun, el primer modelo coreano de la Población Virtual de IT’IS<br>        - "
"Base de datos de materiales<br>        - Scripting en Python y Jupyter "
"Notebook      "

